      <div>
       <h1><a href="/partnerships" title="Colleges &amp;amp; universities, internship sites, donors, etc.">Partnerships</a></h1>
       <p>Colleges &amp; universities, internship sites, donors, etc.</p>
       <div class="item-list menu-list">
        <ul>
         <li class="long">
          <div class="middle">
           <h2><a href="/partnerships/colleges-universities">Colleges &amp; Universities</a></h2>
           <p></p>
           <p></p>
           <p>Partner with TWC to provide students academic semesters, summer terms and seminars in Washington, D.C.</p>
           <p></p>
          </div></li>
         <li class="long">
          <div class="middle">
           <h2><a href="/partnerships/internship-sites">Internship Sites</a></h2>
           <p></p>
           <p></p>
           <p>Give students an invaluable chance to test drive a career by mentoring those who may one day lead an organization or industry.</p>
           <p></p>
          </div></li>
         <li class="long">
          <div class="middle">
           <h2><a href="/partnerships/corporations-foundations">Corporations &amp; Foundations</a></h2>
           <p></p>
           <p></p>
           <p>Join TWC in crafting new experiential learning opportunities through sponsoring scholarships, programs and other essential needs.</p>
           <p></p>
          </div></li>
         <li class="long">
          <div class="middle">
           <h2><a href="/partnerships/governments">Governments</a></h2>
           <p></p>
           <p></p>
           <p>Play a crucial role in helping students become active and engaged leaders in their societies.</p>
           <p></p>
          </div></li>
         <li class="long">
          <div class="middle">
           <h2><a href="/partnerships/alumni-friends">Alumni &amp; Friends</a></h2>
           <p></p>
           <p></p>
           <p>Be a part of TWC’s continuing work by promoting TWC’s programs, recruiting students, or giving towards essential programs.</p>
           <p></p>
          </div></li>
        </ul>
       </div>
